user will click the 'player 1 Draw'

from the facedown cards pile -> reveal a card in the face up card file

display winner or loser in the middle

click player 1 Draw again to display the new from facedown cards pile
the winner will take both faceup cards and add it to the bottom of the facedown cards pile



when you hit the draw the second time add the cards to the end of the winner 

